        {
            "title": "澤連斯基稱很快將與川普會面 暗示和平談判取得進展",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span class=\"news-dateline\">【彭博】--</span> 烏克蘭總統<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link\" data-ylk=\"slk:澤連斯基;sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link;itc:0\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/tag/澤連斯基\">澤連斯基</a>稱計畫在「未來幾天」與美國總統川普會面，暗示他對達成和平協議以結束持續了近四年的俄烏戰事持樂觀態度。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">「許多事情可以在新年前決定，」澤連斯基周五在社交媒體平台Telegram和X上發帖稱。此前，他聽取了烏克蘭首席談判代表烏梅羅夫的最新匯報。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">《基輔郵報》早些時候引述一位知情人士的消息報導，澤連斯基預計最早將於周日前往佛羅里達，川普正在那兒過聖誕假期。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">澤連斯基和川普正尋求就一項20點和平計畫達成一致，以便交由俄羅斯總統普丁。儘管雙方在多數條款上已達成共識，但若干問題仍懸而未決，包括烏克蘭拒絕在東部頓涅茨克地區作出領土讓步。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-7b742076-2d59-39c8-a532-df2c6d39bb40-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">澤連斯基周四表示，他與美國特使史蒂夫·威特科夫和賈裡德·庫什納就和平計畫進行了「非常好的對話」。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題Zelenskiy Says He’ll Meet Trump Soon Signaling Progress on Peace</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2025 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E6%BE%A4%E9%80%A3%E6%96%AF%E5%9F%BA%E7%A8%B1%E5%BE%88%E5%BF%AB%E5%B0%87%E8%88%87%E5%B7%9D%E6%99%AE%E6%9C%83%E9%9D%A2-%E6%9A%97%E7%A4%BA%E5%92%8C%E5%B9%B3%E8%AB%87%E5%88%A4%E5%8F%96%E5%BE%97%E9%80%B2%E5%B1%95-073453673.html",
            "pub_date": "2025-12-26 16:35:55",
            "source": "yahoo_finance_asia",
            "kind": 1,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "現貨黃金和白銀價格升至歷史新高 受地緣政治和美元走軟影響",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">【彭博】— 黃金和白銀價格上漲至歷史新高，地緣政治緊張局勢升級和美元疲弱，助推了貴金屬的歷史性漲勢。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">現貨黃金價格一度上漲1.2%，觸及每盎司4,530美元以上的歷史新高。委內瑞拉局勢摩擦不斷，美國對尼古拉斯·馬杜羅政府施加更大壓力，進一步提升了這種貴金屬的避險吸引力。在非洲，美國對奈及利亞的「伊斯蘭國」組織發動了「強有力的致命打擊」。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">現貨白銀價格連續第五個交易日上漲，漲幅一度高達4.5%，首次突破每盎司75美元大關。近期白銀價格的上漲主要得益於投機性資金流入，以及10月歷史性的逼空後主要交易中心持續存在的供應錯位。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-8f5e556b-138d-38cb-a276-ea32b1e67a99-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">彭博美元指數本周下跌0.8%，創下6月以來最大跌幅。美元走軟通常對黃金和白銀價格構成支撐。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"540\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/VkSWu2VYEaZ2JnOBDsWOMw--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTU0MDtjZj13ZWJw/https://media.zenfs.com/no/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/e6b28d0a36e4721ab1ec7c65eb432970\" width=\"960\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">今年以來黃金價格已上漲約70%，白銀價格上漲超過150%，兩種貴金屬均有望創下自1979年以來的最佳年度表現。強勁上漲行情得益於各國央行加大購入力度，資金流入交易所交易基金（ETF），以及聯儲會連續三次降息。由於貴金屬不支付利息，較低的借貸成本對其構成利好，交易員們預計2026年將進一步降息。</p><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"540\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/QT72uhOu_.qq7zh8XIMI3Q--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTU0MDtjZj13ZWJw/https://media.zenfs.com/no/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/3ab10c9ec4af0e81a3ec81be5e16422b\" width=\"960\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">截至新加坡時間09:25，黃金價格上漲0.8%，至每盎司4,516.70美元。白銀價格上漲4.3%，至每盎司74.94美元。鉑金價格上漲4.8%，逼近周三創下的每盎司2,381.53美元高點，該高點為彭博自1987年開始收集鉑金數據以來的最高水平。鈀金價格上漲4%。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題Gold, Silver Jump to Record Highs on Geopolitics, Weak Dollar</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"cpos:1;pos:1\" data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;cpos:1;pos:1;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com/\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2025 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E7%8F%BE%E8%B2%A8%E9%BB%83%E9%87%91%E5%92%8C%E7%99%BD%E9%8A%80%E5%83%B9%E6%A0%BC%E5%8D%87%E8%87%B3%E6%AD%B7%E5%8F%B2%E6%96%B0%E9%AB%98-%E5%8F%97%E5%9C%B0%E7%B7%A3%E6%94%BF%E6%B2%BB%E5%92%8C%E7%BE%8E%E5%85%83%E8%B5%B0%E8%BB%9F%E5%BD%B1%E9%9F%BF-015445695.html",
            "pub_date": "2025-12-26 12:45:42",
            "source": "yahoo_finance_asia",
            "kind": 1,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "國投瑞銀白銀期貨基金跌停 此前收緊申購規定並多次發布風險提示",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">【彭博】— 周四中國唯一一只以白銀期貨為底層資產的基金跌停，結束了此前瘋狂的上漲行情，基金管理人此前罕見發布了一系列風險提示。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">隨著全球對貴金屬的興趣升溫，國投瑞銀白銀期貨證券投資基金(LOF)數周持續上漲，但基金管理人認為不具備可持續性。周三現貨白銀價格觸及每盎司72.70美元的紀錄高位，並有望創下自1979年以來最佳年度表現。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">本周該基金連續三天漲停後，國投瑞銀基金管理有限公司周三晚間收緊申購規定。根據其在網站發布的公告，該基金C類基金占有率申購限額自12月26日起調整為100元人民幣，A類申購限額仍為500元。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-b8d39c94-e737-345a-aa5b-2708592738b3-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"540\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/dakNxIJvSsX3QDkDM7FQNw--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTU0MDtjZj13ZWJw/https://media.zenfs.com/no/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/da14e12e09d0672353f6878ce57000f8\" width=\"960\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">基金管理人還再次發布基金佔有率二級市場交易價格溢價風險提示，稱投資者如果盲目投資於高溢價率的基金占有率，可能面臨較大損失。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">今年以來，該白銀基金的漲幅已接近220%，而同期上海白銀期貨價格僅上漲約128%。截至周三，該基金相對於底層資產的溢價已接近62%，高於本月初的7%。隨著基金價格下跌和期貨價格繼續上漲，預計周四該溢價水平將有所回落。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">國投瑞銀不予置評。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題China Silver Fund Plunges After String of Moves to Quell Frenzy</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"cpos:1;pos:1\" data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;cpos:1;pos:1;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com/\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2025 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E5%9C%8B%E6%8A%95%E7%91%9E%E9%8A%80%E7%99%BD%E9%8A%80%E6%9C%9F%E8%B2%A8%E5%9F%BA%E9%87%91%E8%B7%8C%E5%81%9C-%E6%AD%A4%E5%89%8D%E6%94%B6%E7%B7%8A%E7%94%B3%E8%B3%BC%E8%A6%8F%E5%AE%9A%E4%B8%A6%E5%A4%9A%E6%AC%A1%E7%99%BC%E5%B8%83%E9%A2%A8%E9%9A%AA%E6%8F%90%E7%A4%BA-082617405.html",
            "pub_date": "2025-12-26 12:05:45",
